text: Amanbek Manybekov (Russian: Аманбек Маныбеков, born 6 August 1995) is a footballer from Kyrgyzstan. He currently plays for Khorezm and the Kyrgyzstan national football team.http://national-football- teams.com/player/65548/Amanbek_Manybekov.html The adaptable defender made his national team debut in the starting eleven against Turkmenistan.http://sport.kg/main_news/35185-amanbek-manybekov-vyzov-v- sbornuyu-snachala-podumal-chto-eto-rozygrysh.html ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Kyrgyzstani footballers Category:Kyrgyzstan international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Footballers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Kyrgyzstan
